Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:17.21,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}HAPPY!!奇怪的朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.21,0:23:20.96,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}就算有些脱节也没关系
